text: Dobromyśl () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kamienna Góra, within Kamienna Góra County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south- western Poland. It lies approximately south of Kamienna Góra, and south-west of the regional capital Wrocław. ==References== Category:Villages in Kamienna Góra County
title: Dobromyśl, Lower Silesian Voivodeship
